OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782026282
OL,3,CCounter-terrorism police involved
OL,4,Cafter five injured in Edinburgh
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FCounter-terrorism officers are
OL,8,Finvolved in investigations into a
OL,9,Fseries of incidents in Edinburgh which
OL,10,Fleft five people injured, police have
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FPolice Scotland said a 36-year-old
OL,14,Fwhite Scottish man has been arrested
OL,15,Fand said and there is no further
OL,16,Fthreat to the public.
OL,18,FOfficers were called to a report of an
OL,19,Fincident in the Sighthill area of the
OL,20,Fcity, where two men were injured, at
OL,21,Faround 8.50pm on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
