OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782026282
OL,3,CCounter-terrorism police involved
OL,4,Cafter five injured in Edinburgh
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FPolice said they then received reports
OL,8,Fabout incidents around retailers
OL,9,Facross the west and north of the city.
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FThe force said that during this period
OL,17,Fthree other men were allegedly
OL,18,Fattacked in the Telford Road and Leith
OL,19,FWalk area.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
