PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782026282
OL,3,CCounter-terrorism police involved
OL,4,Cafter five injured in Edinburgh
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FPolice said that five men, two aged
OL,8,F22, and others aged 24, 27, and 39,
OL,9,Fsustained a range of injuries and
OL,10,Fthree needed hospital treatment,
OL,11,Fhowever none of the injuries are life
OL,12,Fthreatening.
OL,14,FThe organisation Muslim Engagement and
OL,15,FDevelopment (Mend) said that several
OL,16,Fof those injured are Muslim.
OL,18,FPolice said the 36-year-old man was
OL,19,Fdetained at around 9.30pm on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
