PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782026282
OL,3,CCounter-terrorism police involved
OL,4,Cafter five injured in Edinburgh
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FPolice closed off Leith Walk on Friday
OL,8,Fevening as the incidents unfolded,
OL,9,Fwith posts on social media appearing
OL,10,Fto show a man with a knife on the
OL,11,Fstreet.
OL,13,FAnother video appeared to show a
OL,14,Ftopless man on the ground shouting
OL,15,Fthat he is "protecting the country" as
OL,16,Fhe is held by an officer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
