PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782026282
OL,3,CCounter-terrorism police involved
OL,4,Cafter five injured in Edinburgh
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FAssistant Chief Constable Catriona
OL,8,FPaton said it was a "shocking"
OL,9,Fincident and that her thoughts are
OL,10,Fwith those who were injured and most
OL,11,Fdirectly affected.
OL,13,FShe said: "I want to send a clear
OL,14,Fmessage of support to all our
OL,15,Fcommunities that there is no place for
OL,16,Fracism or faith-based hate in a
OL,17,FScotland which is at its best when we
OL,18,Fstand together.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
