PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782026282
OL,3,CCounter-terrorism police involved
OL,4,Cafter five injured in Edinburgh
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,F"Officers responded to multiple
OL,8,Freports of a fast-moving sequence of
OL,9,Fevents across Edinburgh before
OL,10,Farresting a man and public safety was
OL,11,Four priority.
OL,13,F"Extensive work is ongoing to
OL,14,Festablish all the circumstances.
OL,16,F"We are being supported by Counter
OL,17,FTerrorism Policing and working under
OL,18,Fthe direction of the Crown Office and
OL,19,FProcurator Fiscal Service.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
