PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782026282
OL,3,CCounter-terrorism police involved
OL,4,Cafter five injured in Edinburgh
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,F"I want to thank our officers who
OL,8,Fresponded with bravery and
OL,9,Fprofessionalism, and with a focus on
OL,10,Fprotecting the public."
OL,12,FI'm hugely grateful for the support
OL,13,Fand assistance of our communities and
OL,14,Fwould appeal for anyone with any
OL,15,Finformation to share it with police.
OL,17,F"We have established a major incident
OL,18,Fpolice portal."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
